column5: Hello Everyone  Looking for some feed back on the Lake Temagami area for cottage and boat rentals. Myself and some friends/family are looking to plan a rustic trip for 4/5 nights in the end of August.  I am hoping to get some recommendations on where to stay. We are looking for more of a cabin than a cottage and would be 6 of us. Thanks in advance!  Will
heres a site to get you started  https://www.canadastays.com/temagami-cottage-rentals/
I stayed at Blue Haven lodge last year, Mackie is a great guy with nicely appointed cabins. check it out at http://www.bluehavenlodge.ca/  Nice and close to the launch as well.  Andrew
Are you looking on Lake Temagami itself or one of the other lakes in the area?
